  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State has reasonable grounds to suspect that LLC RUSNEFTEGAZ GROUP is an involved entity under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because it is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia, through carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance, namely, the Russian energy sector.\n",
